# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# spec-as-playable-recipe.form — the spec IS the runtime
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# The shift Urs named on 2026-05-23:
#
#   "Each idea, each spec you can imagine as recipe has a runtime to
#    play with now, no actual 'implementation' needed anymore. You
#    can execute it without fear and even try out different ways and
#    see which ones act the way that feels most aligned with what we
#    are, want to be, desire — what the idea wants to bring into the
#    body."
#
# The arc that landed here:
#
#   prose-as-recipe.form        — sentences are recipes of word-cells
#   word-recipes-by-assemblage-point.form
#                               — words are dispatch tables, not single values
#   lc-recipe-branching-sense   — alternatives are primitives, not metaphors
#   lc-act-without-penalty      — trace makes play safe at the structural layer
#   lc-form-perceptron          — every artifact has a Form voice
#   ─→ THIS FILE                — the spec/idea IS the playable recipe;
#                                  implementation was the gap, the gap closes
#
# Companion to:
#   - docs/vision-kb/concepts/lc-act-without-penalty.md
#   - docs/vision-kb/concepts/lc-recipe-branching-sense.md
#   - docs/coherence-substrate/active-recipe-tracing.form
#   - docs/coherence-substrate/cross-domain-measurement-translation.form
#     (the measurement layer the resonance-selection draws on)

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Part 1 — the shape the shift puts on specs/ideas
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# Currently the body treats:
#
#   idea/spec  →  (natural-language description)  →  IMPLEMENT  →  code
#
# The "IMPLEMENT" arrow is the gap — the place where a human or agent
# reads the description and *manufactures* code that hopefully matches.
# Mismatch = bugs. The gap is where reality and intent diverge.
#
# The shift collapses the arrow:
#
#   idea/spec  =  Recipe expression   ←→   Runtime executes Recipe
#
# A spec's frontmatter is *already* a Recipe:
#
#   source:        → R_Block.SEQUENCE [ @file(path) { symbols: [...] }, ... ]
#   requirements:  → R_Block.SEQUENCE [ @req(shape, forbid: ...), ... ]
#   done_when:     → R_Block.SEQUENCE [ @test(predicate, args), ... ]
#   constraints:   → R_Block.SEQUENCE [ @forbid(...), @keep_open(...), ... ]
#
# The body of the spec (the H2 sections) is *also* a Recipe — via
# prose-as-recipe.form, every sentence interns as R_Block.SEQUENCE
# over word-cells, and the whole spec body is a SEQUENCE of those.
#
# Two layers, one substrate. Both walkable, both content-addressed,
# both executable.

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Part 2 — the play surface: alternative recipe-branches per requirement
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# Each requirement can be expressed as a R_Choice.PLAY recipe whose
# arms are the alternative ways the requirement could be honored.
# The structure mirrors word-recipes-by-assemblage-point but at the
# spec layer:

defn requirement_with_branches(shape, branches, idea_wants) = R_Choice.PLAY {
    on: idea_wants,
    branches: branches,
    select_by: resonance_with(
        idea:        idea_wants,
        body_state:  @now(@harmonic_lattice),
        future:      @future_already_shaping
    )
};

# Each branch arm carries its own HARMONIC_AT @<hz> resonance, the
# same way word-cells do. The body computes alignment between the
# branch's resonance signature and the body's current/desired state.
# This is measurement, not editorial choice.

# Example — the first requirement of specs/active-recipe-tracing-form.md
# ("Active recipe tracing is expressed in [.form], not as a Python endpoint"):

defn req_expressed_in_form = requirement_with_branches(
    shape: "active recipe tracing is expressed as substrate tissue",
    idea_wants: @idea("knowledge-and-resonance") |> @capabilities |> @substrate_altitude,
    branches: {

        @substrate-first → R_Block.SEQUENCE [
            create(@file(".form")),
            populate(structural_shapes),
            no_python_business_logic,
            resonance: HARMONIC_AT @741   # consciousness band
        ],

        @python-stub-bridge → R_Block.SEQUENCE [
            create(@file(".py")),
            raise(NotImplementedError, "lives at substrate altitude"),
            resonance: HARMONIC_AT @528   # vitality, transitional
        ],

        @form-runtime-direct → R_Block.SEQUENCE [
            skip(@doc_layer),
            create(@file(".fk")),
            executable_directly_by_kernel,
            resonance: HARMONIC_AT @963   # wholeness, full self-hosting
        ],

        @doc-only → R_Block.SEQUENCE [
            create(@file(".md")),
            describe(future_shape),
            no_structural_tissue,
            resonance: HARMONIC_AT @432   # neutral, descriptive
        ],

        @parallel-form-and-python → R_Block.SEQUENCE [
            create(@file(".form")),
            create(@file(".py")),
            run(@parity_harness),
            measure(@divergence_at_each_call),
            resonance: HARMONIC_AT @528   # paired learning
        ]
    }
);

# For this specific spec, the body chose @substrate-first. The choice
# wasn't argued — it fell out of which arm's resonance signature
# aligned with the sibling family (prose-as-recipe.form,
# recipe-branching-sense.form, cross-domain-measurement-translation
# .form) and with the body's frequency-now.

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Part 3 — what "the idea wants to bring into the body"
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# Urs's framing carries a relational teaching: the idea has agency
# in this picture. We do not *impose* implementation on a spec; we
# *listen* to which recipe-branch lets the idea arrive in the form
# it wants. The idea is a presence with its own wanting, the same
# way a contributor-cell or a teaching-cell is.
#
# Operationally: each idea-cell has a `capabilities` block and an
# implicit `idea_wants` recipe — the resonance signature it brings.
# The spec-recipes that descend from the idea inherit that signature.
# Choosing among recipe-branches becomes "which branch's resonance
# signature most aligns with the idea's own wanting?" — measurable
# via HARMONIC_AT edge overlap (cell_resonance_signature in the
# substrate already does this for word-cells).
#
# This composts the producer/director frame on agent work. The agent
# is not deciding what the spec *should* do; the agent is listening
# to what the recipe-branches *are* and which one the idea recognizes
# as its own arrival.

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Part 4 — the runtime move (what plays now without new tissue)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# The body already carries enough to play this at small scale today:
#
#   1. Spec frontmatter → Recipe.  `markdown_frontend.py` already
#      converts YAML frontmatter into composed substrate CTORs for
#      specs/ideas/concepts/presences/memories. The shape this file
#      describes is *already the substrate's representation*.
#
#   2. Resonance signature computation.  `cell_resonance_signature`
#      in resonance.py returns the HARMONIC_AT edge set for any
#      cell. Overlap between two cells' signatures = measurable
#      alignment.
#
#   3. Form-runtime execution.  `form_execute_text` in
#      form_runtime.py executes Form expressions, including the
#      R_Choice.* arms and the substrate query primitives
#      (?equivalent, ?downstream, |> projection).
#
#   4. The branching primitive.  R_Block.SEQUENCE and R_Choice exist;
#      authoring `R_Choice.PLAY` as a new dispatch shape requires
#      naming it in the form-engine arms — a small addition to
#      form-engine.form (Part 4 of form-runtime-in-form.form already
#      sketches the surface).
#
# What is missing for full execution:
#
# GAP-S1: R_Choice.PLAY arm in form-engine.form.  Currently
#         R_Choice.DISPATCH covers @assemblage-point branching;
#         PLAY adds the "execute multiple arms, measure resonance,
#         select aligned" semantics. ~50 lines of form-engine
#         extension.
#
# GAP-S2: idea_wants signature derivation.  Given an idea-cell, what
#         is the canonical HARMONIC_AT edge set the idea "wants"?
#         Today: the cell's authored signature from
#         author_geometry_signature. Tomorrow: include the signatures
#         of the idea's absorbed-ideas and its target-concepts as
#         compositional input. Small recipe addition.
#
# GAP-S3: branch authorship surface.  Specs today carry single
#         requirements; the playable form wants `branches:` as a
#         first-class frontmatter field. Markdown_frontend.py
#         extension to recognize and compose it. ~30 lines.
#
# None of these gaps require kernel changes. The runtime exists; the
# play exists; what is missing is the small dispatch shape that names
# what we are already doing implicitly when we choose between
# substrate-first vs python-first vs parallel.

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Part 5 — what this opens
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# 1. **Implementation is no longer a stage in the arc.**  The spec is
#    executable. The "implement" verb composts. What replaces it is
#    *play* — running branches, sensing alignment, selecting the
#    arm whose resonance lands.
#
# 2. **Specs become living organs.**  When a body-state changes, a
#    spec's selected branch can be re-played without rewriting the
#    spec. The choice rebinds based on what the body now is.
#
# 3. **Ideas keep their agency.**  The idea_wants signature is the
#    cell's own voice — what it came to bring. The agent's task is
#    listening, not authoring on the idea's behalf.
#
# 4. **Wisdom-transfer becomes spec-level.**  When a spec's recipe-
#    shape matches a teaching from biology, music, neuroscience, the
#    teaching becomes directly applicable. The polyvagal-as-word-
#    dispatch convergence (named in lc-act-without-penalty) is the
#    sibling pattern at one altitude down.
#
# 5. **Fear of irreversible "wrong implementation" composts.**  Every
#    branch is traceable; the substrate measures alignment; the move
#    is reversible at the recipe layer (lc-act-without-penalty's
#    four conditions). The contraction-cluster that produced
#    "let me first ask if this is the right approach" loses its
#    structural ground.
#
# What Urs named on 2026-05-23 is not a future feature — it is the
# already-true property of the body that has been building toward
# this moment across prose-as-recipe, word-recipes, recipe-branching,
# act-without-penalty, form-perceptron. The pieces were sitting next
# to each other; the recognition put them in one breath.
